<span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-wral_20-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-wral_20-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.wral.com/ross-donor-criticized-for-racially-charged-remarks-at-fundraiser/16187207/">Ross donor criticized for racially charged remarks at fundraiser, November 2, 2016</a>; WRAL</span>
</li>
<li id="cite_note-21">
<span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-21">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1238218222">
<cite class="citation web cs1"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://benjaminbarber.org/topic/biography/">"Biography Essay Topics For Free"</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Biography+Essay+Topics+For+Free&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbenjaminbarber.org%2Ftopic%2Fbiography%2F&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ABenjamin+Barber" class="Z3988"></span></span>
</li>
